# Changelog

The general format of entries is:
<tag> <yyyy>-<mm>-<dd> <author>
    <#> - [new/fix/bug-fix/draft/dependency] <description of the fix, feature or change>
        - <webapp path 1>
        - <webapp path 2>
        - *


